lly involved can handle the moderation.<br><br>Furthermore there will be no moderation based on opinions on this server. None whatsoever. We do not like censorship, and will only delete obvious spam, harassment, etc, and only when/if it's really necessary. No admin will be allowed discriminate anyone or give any special privileges to friends. We do not regard this board as ours but as the whole server community's, and we try our best to act accordingly. <br><br>The team that manage this board consist of the following people, in no particular order:<br><br>Edeina<br>A magician who left her guild behind on SolRo. Journalist IRL.<br><br>Kivorn<br>A ranger from SolRo. Newsman of The Ranger's Glade. Student/Journalist IRL.<br><br>Jzonn<br>A ranger from Karana.<br><br>Edit: we are so far four persons who work on this particular board, but we are likely to add more people soon. The old list was a bit premature, I included a person who was part of the initial initiative and I thus assumed would be part of the team when we started working on this board. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0> at: 7/27/01 5:52:10 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Board Mistress</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/21/00 11:19:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A note from Kivorn sums it up quite nicely</span><hr size=1> Policy: We won't interfere in the community, but let the topics 